From: Kazuya Mizuguchi <kazuya.mizuguchi.ks@renesas.com>
Date: Mon, 30 May 2016 05:25:43 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 0853/2066] ravb: Add SET_RUNTIME_PM_OPS macro

upstream 524c6f691b99065577b245b250efe93fb0cda5c4 commit

Use SET_RUNTIME_PM_OPS macro instead of assigning a member of
dev_pm_ops directly.

Signed-off-by: Kazuya Mizuguchi <kazuya.mizuguchi.ks@renesas.com>
Signed-off-by: Yoshihiro Kaneko <ykaneko0929@gmail.com>
Acked-by: Sergei Shtylyov <sergei.shtylyov@cogentembedded.com>
Signed-off-by: David S. Miller <davem@davemloft.net>
---
 drivers/net/ethernet/renesas/ravb_main.c |    3 +--
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/net/ethernet/renesas/ravb_main.c b/drivers/net/ethernet/renesas/ravb_main.c
index 092db6a..8986f95 100644
--- a/drivers/net/ethernet/renesas/ravb_main.c
+++ b/drivers/net/ethernet/renesas/ravb_main.c
@@ -2125,8 +2125,7 @@ static int ravb_runtime_nop(struct device *dev)
 }
 
 static const struct dev_pm_ops ravb_dev_pm_ops = {
-	.runtime_suspend = ravb_runtime_nop,
-	.runtime_resume = ravb_runtime_nop,
+	SET_RUNTIME_PM_OPS(ravb_runtime_nop, ravb_runtime_nop, NULL)
 };
 
 #define RAVB_PM_OPS (&ravb_dev_pm_ops)
